{%- comment -%}
  ============================================================================
  Design System · Section: Kategorie-Leiste (fs-category-chips)
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Kontextabhängige, horizontal scrollbare Kategorie-Leiste unter dem Header.

  - Auf einer Sportwelt (/pages/welt-*): zeigt automatisch die Unterkategorien
    der aktuellen Sportart aus dem Menü (z. B. Tischtennis → Beläge, Hölzer …)
    plus optional einen Sale-Chip.
  - Sonst (Root/Chooser etc.): zeigt die Top-Ebene des Menüs.

  Das aktuelle Sport-Menü wird über den URL-Pfad erkannt (Top-Menüpunkt, dessen
  Link im Pfad enthalten ist und der Unterpunkte hat). Rein Liquid/CSS.
  ============================================================================
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign accent = section.settings.accent_color | default: '#486A8F'
  assign uid = section.id | replace: '_', '' | replace: '-', ''
  assign menu = linklists[section.settings.menu]
  assign path = request.path
  assign current = null

  comment
    1) Aktuelle Sportwelt über die Welt-Seite erkennen (z. B. /pages/welt-tischtennis).
  endcomment
  for link in menu.links
    if link.links.size > 0 and link.url != '/' and link.url != blank
      if path == link.url or path contains link.url
        assign current = link
      endif
    endif
  endfor

  comment
    2) Sonst über eine aktive Unterkategorie erkennen – so bleibt die Sport-Leiste
    auch auf Kollektionsseiten (z. B. /collections/hoelzer) und darunter erhalten.
  endcomment
  unless current
    for link in menu.links
      if link.links.size > 0
        for sub in link.links
          if sub.url != '/' and sub.url != blank
            assign sub_prefix = sub.url | append: '/'
            if path == sub.url or path contains sub_prefix
              assign current = link
            endif
          endif
        endfor
      endif
    endfor
  endunless
-%}

{%- style -%}
  .fs-chips--{{ uid }} { --fs-chips-accent: var(--fs-sport-accent, {{ accent }}); }
  @media (max-width: {{ section.settings.desktop_hide_below | default: 990 }}px) { }
{%- endstyle -%}

<style>
  .fs-chips { border-block: 1px solid rgba(128,128,128,.14); background: var(--fs-chips-bg, transparent); }
  {%- unless section.settings.show_on_desktop -%}
  @media (min-width: 990px) { .fs-chips--{{ uid }} { display: none; } }
  {%- endunless -%}
  .fs-chips__scroll {
    display: flex; gap: clamp(1rem, 4vw, 1.75rem); align-items: center;
    max-width: var(--page-width, 1400px); margin-inline: auto;
    padding: .7rem var(--page-margin, 1rem);
    overflow-x: auto; scrollbar-width: none; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
  }
  .fs-chips__scroll::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .fs-chips__item {
    flex: none; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; font-weight: 600;
    font-size: .95rem; white-space: nowrap; padding-bottom: .3rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .fs-chips__item:hover { color: var(--fs-chips-accent); }
  .fs-chips__item.is-active { color: var(--fs-chips-accent); border-bottom-color: var(--fs-chips-accent); }
  .fs-chips__item--sale { color: var(--fs-chips-accent); }
  .fs-chips__item:focus-visible { outline: 3px solid var(--fs-chips-accent); outline-offset: 3px; border-radius: 4px; }
</style>

<nav class="fs-chips fs-chips--{{ uid }}" aria-label="{{ section.settings.aria_label | default: 'Kategorien' }}">
  <div class="fs-chips__scroll">
    {%- if current -%}
      {%- if section.settings.show_sale and section.settings.sale_url != blank -%}
        <a class="fs-chips__item fs-chips__item--sale" href="{{ section.settings.sale_url }}">{{ section.settings.sale_label | default: 'Sale' }}</a>
      {%- endif -%}
      {%- for sub in current.links -%}
        <a class="fs-chips__item{% if sub.current or request.path == sub.url %} is-active{% endif %}" href="{{ sub.url }}">{{ sub.title }}</a>
      {%- endfor -%}
    {%- else -%}
      {%- for link in menu.links -%}
        <a class="fs-chips__item{% if link.current %} is-active{% endif %}" href="{{ link.url }}">{{ link.title }}</a>
      {%- endfor -%}
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>
</nav>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Kategorie-Leiste",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "fs-section",
  "settings": [
    { "type": "link_list", "id": "menu", "label": "Menü", "default": "main-menu" },
    { "type": "checkbox", "id": "show_on_desktop", "label": "Auch auf Desktop zeigen", "default": false },
    { "type": "header", "content": "Sale-Chip (auf Sportwelten)" },
    { "type": "checkbox", "id": "show_sale", "label": "Sale-Chip zeigen", "default": true },
    { "type": "text", "id": "sale_label", "label": "Sale – Text", "default": "Sale" },
    { "type": "url", "id": "sale_url", "label": "Sale – Link" },
    { "type": "header", "content": "Farbe" },
    { "type": "color", "id": "accent_color", "label": "Akzentfarbe (Futurespin-Blau)", "default": "#486A8F" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "aria_label", "label": "ARIA-Label", "default": "Kategorien" }
  ],
  "presets": [ { "name": "Kategorie-Leiste" } ]
}
{% endschema %}
